7","c":"وَاحِدَةٌ","d":"wāḥidatun","e":"ٌẗَdِḥَٰw"},{"b":"7.0","h":"8.89","c":"كَلَمْحٍ","d":"kalamḥin","e":"ٍۭḥْmَlَk"},{"b":"9.0","h":"11.35","c":"بِالْبَصَرِ","d":"bil-baṣari","e":"ِrَṣَbْlٱِb"}],"a":{"g":"And Our command is but one, like a glance of the eye."}},"51":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.2","c":"وَلَقَدْ","d":"walaqad","e":"ْdَqَlَw"},{"b":"0.82","h":"1.3","c":"أَهْلَكْنَا","d":"ahlaknā","e":"ٓāَnْkَlْhَaʾ"},{"b":"3.2","h":"3.2","c":"أَشْيَاعَكُمْ","d":"ashyāʿakum","e":"ْmُkَʿعāَyْhsَaʾ"},{"b":"4.8","h":"7.61","c":"فَهَلْ","d":"fahal","e":"ْlَhَf"},{"b":"5.5","h":"8.91","c":"مِنْ","d":"min","e":"nِm"},{"b":"6.9","h":"10.37","c":"مُدَّكِرٍ","d":"muddakirin","e":"ٍrِkَّdُّm"}],"a":{"g":"And We have already destroyed your kinds, so is there any who will remember?"}},"52":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.17","c":"وَكُلُّ","d":"wakullu","e":"ُّlُkَw"},{"b":"0.86","h":"1.57","c":"شَيْءٍ","d":"shayin","e":"ٍءْàَhs"},{"b":"2.4","h":"3.62","c":"فَعَلُوهُ","d":"faʿalūhu","e":"ُhwُlَʿعَf"},{"b":"3.6","h":"5.57","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"àِf"},{"b":"3.8","h":"5.96","c":"الزُّبُرِ","d":"l-zuburi","e":"ِrُbُّzlٱ"}],"a":{"g":"And everything they did is in written records."}},"53":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.26","c":"وَكُلُّ","d":"wakullu","e":"ُّlُkَw"},{"b":"0.83","h":"1.65","c":"صَغِيرٍ","d":"ṣaghīrin","e":"ٍryِغَṣ"},{"b":"1.8","h":"3.99","c":"وَكَبِيرٍ","d":"wakabīrin","e":"ٍryِbَkَw"},{"b":"4.5","h":"7.08","c":"مُسْتَطَرٌ","d":"mus'taṭarun","e":"ٌrَṭَtْsُّm"}],"a":{"g":"And every small and great [thing] is inscribed."}},"54":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.03","c":"إِنَّ","d":"inna","e":"َّnِiʾ"},{"b":"1.3","h":"1.51","c":"الْمُتَّقِينَ","d":"l-mutaqīna","e":"َnyِqَّtُmْlٱ"},{"b":"2.8","h":"4.15","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"àِf"},{"b":"3.3","h":"5.07","c":"جَنَّاتٍ","d":"jannātin","e":"ٍtَّٰnَjg"},{"b":"5.3","h":"8.42","c":"وَنَهَرٍ","d":"wanaharin","e":"ٍrَhَnَw"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed, the righteous will be among gardens and rivers,"}},"55":{"w":[{"b":"0.04","h":"0.03","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"àِf"},{"b":"0.52","h":"0.66","c":"مَقْعَدِ","d":"maqʿadi","e":"ِdَʿعْqَm"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.13","c":"صِدْقٍ","d":"ṣid'qin","e":"ٍqْdِṣ"},{"b":"2.4","h":"3.71","c":"عِنْدَ","d":"ʿinda","e":"َdnِʿع"},{"b":"3.6","h":"5.59","c":"مَلِيكٍ","d":"malīkin","e":"ٍkyِlَm"},{"b":"6.0","h":"8.22","c":"مُقْتَدِرٍ","d":"muq'tadirin","e":"ٍۭrِdَtْqُّm"}],"a":{"g":"In a seat of honor near a Sovereign, Perfect in Ability.","ihya":"<div class='ihya-container' style='margin-top: 20px; padding: 15px; background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #d4af37; border-radius: 4px;'><h4 style='color: #d4af37; margin-bottom: 15px; font-family: \"Cinzel\", serif;'>Ihya 'Ulum al-Din Commentary</h4><div class='ihya-entry'><span class='badge badge-light' style='color: #666; border: 1px solid #ddd; margin-bottom: 8px;'>Vol4 book6</span><div class='ihya-text' style='font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;'>Indeed, he whose aim is the Lord of the Abode [rabb al-dar] and the Possessor of Sovereignty [malik al-mulk], and who is overcome by nothing but His love through sincerity [ikhlas] and truthfulness [sidq], He will cause to dwell \"in a seat of truth [fi maq'ad sidq], near a Sovereign Omnipotent [mulk muqtadir].\" Thus, the righteous [al-abrar] will roam in gardens and delight in paradises with wide-eyed maidens and immortal youths. But those brought near [al-muqarrabun] are constant in the Presence [al-hadra], their gaze fixed upon It, and they deem the bliss of the gardens insignificant compared to an atom of It. For some people are preoccupied with satisfying the appetite of the belly and the private parts, while others are for intimate companionship [mujalasa]. And for this reason, the Messenger of God, peace and blessings be upon him, said: \"The majority of the inhabitants of Paradise are the simple-minded, and 'Illiyyun is for those of intellect.\" And when understandings fell short of grasping the meaning of 'Illiyyun, He magnified its matter, saying: \"And what will make you know what 'Illiyyun is?\" just as the Almighty has said: \"The Striking Calamity! What is the Striking Calamity? And what will make you know what the Striking Calamity is?\"</div></div></div>"}}}